Please see the [Using GO for volunteers webpage.](https://www.girlguiding.org.uk/go-for-volunteers/){:.external-link}{:rel="noopener"}{:target="_blank"}

If the problem you are experiencing is not covered here, please contact HQ via <membershipsystems@girlguiding.org.uk> for login issues.

For anything else, in the first instance please contact <membership@girlguidinghertfordshire.org.uk> for assistance.

Your local commissioner should be able to advise you, or you can contact the county treasurer on <ctreasurer@girlguidinghertfordshire.org.uk>

Applications forms for county grants can be found on the website&rsquo;s [Forms page.](/about-us/resources/#grant-applications)

Information about national and regional grants and bursaries can be found on the [Girlguiding UK website](https://www.girlguiding.org.uk/information-for-volunteers/running-your-unit/finance-insurance-and-property/grants-and-funding/){:.external-link}{:rel="noopener"}{:target="_blank"} and the [Girlguiding Anglia website.](https://www.girlguiding-anglia.org.uk/grants-and-applications){:.external-link}{:rel="noopener"}{:target="_blank"}

Sign into your GO account.

From the top right drop down menu, select marketing preferences.  Tick to receive communication by email as well as regional information

